                              <p align="justify">Mr. Sudath Manjula Amarasena is a senior lecturer attached to the Department of Decision Science, University of Sri Jayewardenepura specialized in Operations Research, Operations Management, Commercial and Business Law and Marketing. He has published several books related to the above areas of specialization. Sudath is a gold medalist and has been awarded several occasions for his outstanding performance as an academic in the University of Sri Jayewardenepura. He is an experienced lecturer for several Universities in the country including the University of Sabaragamuwa, Moratuwa and Sri Jayewardenepura.   

